author: Dana Eisenberg
title: Leslie Jones on Milo: ‘You Guys are Giving Him Too Much Energy’
text:
Leslie Jones on Milo: ‘You Guys are Giving Him Too Much Energy’ by Dana Eisenberg | 11:04 am, February 21st, 2017 
Leslie Jones has had just about enough of Milo Yiannopoulos , and she’s responding to the latest controversy surrounding him by telling her Twitter followers that she’s so over it, and has been for a while. “You guys are giving him too much energy,” she writes. “I was done the day I blocked him & got his ass banned. Been done and moved on. He has no space here!” You guys are giving him to much energy. I was done the day I blocked him & got his ass banned. Been done and moved on. He has no space here! 
— Leslie Jones (@Lesdoggg) February 21, 2017 
Yiannopoulos was banned from the social media platform for his “targeted abuse of individuals,” which included calling Jones “illiterate.”
